title: Bricklin - Hetman Kiko's Tomb
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

[[Hetman Emrys Kiko]] was burried in [[Bricklin]]. His tomb is a large structure carved from living rock, that extends from the ground of the city to the overhanging cliff rock 50 feet above. It is one of the major supports for the cut rock. In front of the tomb there is a large square where Bricklin's Den' Orda celebration takes place.